She's been verbally and emotionally abusive my entire life and for the last 10 years I've kept her at arm's length, seeing her only for holidays and birthdays, because I didn't have the guts to fully cut her off.
But now it's finally done and it's a huge weight of my shoulders. Part of me feels guilty and I just need to remind myself that she brought this upon herself by refusing to apologize for or even acknowledge any of her wrongdoings. 
